article_title: Obama Admin. Admits Medicaid Expansion Costs More Than Projected

article_metadata.author: Michael F. Cannon

og.description: The feds had projected newly eligible Medicaid enrollees would cost about $50 less than other Medicaid-enrolled adults, but they actually cost nearly $1,000 more.
